title: Beanbag Natural Health
description: The Beanbag is a small, well stocked family run health food store with a wide range of vegetarian, vegan, and special diet products. Find flours, dried fruit, nuts, seeds, grains, beans and lentils, pasta & rice, herbal and fruit teas, coffees, coffee substitutes plus frozen & chilled items, nut butters, tahini, oils, vinegars, dairy-free milk, chocolate, cakes, desserts, a range of gluten free goods, natural bodycare products. No fresh produce.
